source.name: State of Oklahoma General Revenue Trends, Income vs. Expenditures
source.description: Data showing general revenue trends for the State of Oklahoma for fiscal years 2006 to 2017. Annual revenue estimates will be updated after official release of documents from the December meeting of the State Board of Equalization. Amounts are displayed in millions
